 0104: 
 0105:     # schedule
 0106:     # each time slot has four entries
 0107:     # timeslot type - generation type - activity id - facility id
 0108:     # for example:
 0109:     # (1 - 0 - 1 - 1243) means:
 0110:     # routine - graph facility - edu - 1243
 0111: 
 0112:     # time slot types: (empty, flexible, routine, sleep, transit)
 0113:     # empty - for schedule creation and temporary filling
 0114:     # flexible - flex time, gets re-generated randomly each week
 0115:     # routine - work, edu at this time, is done every day, doesnt change from week to week
 0116:     # sleep - fixed, does not change based on any simulation input
 0117:     # transit - always before and after facility changes, should be automatically generated
 0118:
